<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA526_03_IH_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema526_03.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema526_03_ih_0003">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="3" lang="y">주안이네 모둠이 받은 칭찬 도장 수를 나타낸 표입니다. 물음에 답해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page">
          <h3 class="title" lang="y">주안이네 모둠이 받은 칭찬 도장은 모두 몇 개인가요?</h3>
          <div class="tit_data">
            <div class="inner">
              <span lang="y">학생별 받은 칭찬 도장 수</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="table_wrap row">
            <table>
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="col" lang="y">이름</th>
                  <td lang="y">주안</td>
                  <td lang="y">성민</td>
                  <td lang="y">채아</td>
                  <td lang="y">세연</td>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="row" lang="y">칭찬 도장 수(개)</th>
                  <td>11</td>
                  <td>9</td>
                  <td>14</td>
                  <td>10</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div class="question_box justify_center gap_4" lang="y">
            (
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="44"></math-field>
            </div>
            )개
          </div>
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">(받은 칭찬 도장 수의 합)=11+9+14+10=44(개)</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page">
          <h3 class="title" lang="y">주안이네 모둠의 학생은 모두 몇 명인가요?</h3>
          <div class="tit_data">
            <div class="inner">
              <span lang="y">학생별 받은 칭찬 도장 수</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="table_wrap row">
            <table>
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="col" lang="y">이름</th>
                  <td lang="y">주안</td>
                  <td lang="y">성민</td>
                  <td lang="y">채아</td>
                  <td lang="y">세연</td>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="row" lang="y">칭찬 도장 수(개)</th>
                  <td>11</td>
                  <td>9</td>
                  <td>14</td>
                  <td>10</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div class="question_box justify_center gap_4" lang="y">
            (
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
            </div>
            )명
          </div>
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">주안이네 모둠 학생은 모두 4명입니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page">
          <h3 class="title" lang="y">주안이네 모둠이 받은 칭찬 도장 수의 평균은 몇 개인가요?</h3>
          <div class="tit_data">
            <div class="inner">
              <span lang="y">학생별 받은 칭찬 도장 수</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="table_wrap row">
            <table>
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="col" lang="y">이름</th>
                  <td lang="y">주안</td>
                  <td lang="y">성민</td>
                  <td lang="y">채아</td>
                  <td lang="y">세연</td>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <th scope="row" lang="y">칭찬 도장 수(개)</th>
                  <td>11</td>
                  <td>9</td>
                  <td>14</td>
                  <td>10</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div class="question_box justify_center gap_4" lang="y">
            (
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="11"></math-field>
            </div>
            )개
          </div>
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">(받은 칭찬 도장 수의 평균)=44÷4=11(개)</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
